<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TNT21">
<l>maivaṇṇa naṟuṅkuñci kuḻalpiṉ tāḻa</l>
<l>makarañcēr kuḻaiyirupā ṭilaṅki yāṭa</l>
<l>eyvaṇṇa veñcilaiyē tuṇaiyā viṅkē</l>
<l>yiruvarāy vantāreṉ muṉṉē niṉṟār</l>
<l>kaivaṇṇan tāmaraivāy kamalam pōluṅ</l>
<l>kaṇṇiṇaiyu maravinta maṭiyu maḵtē</l>
<l>avvaṇṇat tavarnilaimai kaṇṭun tōḻī</l>
<l>yavarainān tēvareṉ ṟañci ṉōmē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>As a lock of fragrant kohl-colored curls hung at the back</l>
<l rend="indent">[and] as earrings with makara danced, shining at both sides,</l>
<l>[With] only an arrow-worthy cruel bow as [his] companion,</l>
<l rend="indent">they both came here and stood before me.</l>
<l>The color of his hands, [like] lotuses, a lotus[-like] mouth,</l>
<l rend="indent">and lotuses - both eyes - and feet, too, were that;</l>
<l>Even though we saw the reality of him [with] such beauty, friend,</l>
<l rend="indent">thinking him a “god,” we were frightened.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
